OL,3,COfwat planning independent monitor for
OL,4,CThames Water after ratings downgrades
OL,6,FOfwat said on Wednesday that it
OL,7,Fintends to appoint an independent
OL,8,Fmonitor to Thames Water who will
OL,9,Fsupervise the company's turnaround
OL,10,Fplan and report back to the regulator.
OL,12,FThe monitor would have access to the
OL,13,Fcompany's financial information, and
OL,14,Fthe appointment comes after Thames'
OL,15,Fcredit rating was downgraded twice by
OL,16,Fratings agencies in July, which
OL,17,Fconstitutes a breach of its licence to
OL,18,Foperate, the regulator said.
