OL,3,COfwat planning independent monitor for
OL,4,CThames Water after ratings downgrades
OL,6,FAgreeing to a monitor is one of four
OL,7,Fcommitments Ofwat wants Thames to
OL,8,Fcomply with, which also include
OL,9,Fdeveloping a "suitable" business plan
OL,10,Fto turn around the struggling business.
OL,12,FThe watchdog said Thames must agree to
OL,13,F"taking the steps required to deliver
OL,14,Fan equity raise", and appointing new
OL,15,Fnon-executive directors to its board.
