OL,3,COfwat planning independent monitor for
OL,4,CThames Water after ratings downgrades
OL,6,FOfwat chief executive David Black
OL,7,Fsaid: "We are clear that Thames Water
OL,8,Fneeds to remedy its licence breach,
OL,9,Fturn around its operational
OL,10,Fperformance, and secure backing from
OL,11,Finvestors to restore its loss of
OL,12,Finvestment grade credit rating.
OL,14,F"These enforceable commitments will
OL,15,Finclude our putting an independent
OL,16,Fmonitor into the business, to report
OL,17,Fback to us on what is happening to
OL,18,Fdrive meaningful change in
OL,19,Fperformance, and to ensure appropriate
OL,20,Fexpertise is added to their board.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
