OL,3,COfwat planning independent monitor for
OL,4,CThames Water after ratings downgrades
OL,6,F"We will continue to monitor progress
OL,7,Fvery closely and will not hesitate to
OL,8,Ftake any further action if necessary."
OL,10,FUnder the plan, which is currently up
OL,11,Ffor consultation, the commitments
OL,12,Fwould remain in place until the
OL,13,Fcompany regains two investment grade
OL,14,Fcredit ratings.
OL,16,FMoody's downgraded its rating for
OL,17,FThames to "junk" status on July 24,
OL,18,Findicating that the credit agency
OL,19,Fthinks the utility company is likely
OL,20,Fto default on its debt and may add to
OL,21,Fits financial pressures.
