OL,3,COfwat planning independent monitor for
OL,4,CThames Water after ratings downgrades
OL,6,FAnd on July 31, S&P downgraded Thames
OL,7,FWater's Class A debt rating to BB and
OL,8,Fits Class B debt rating to B.
OL,10,FThe measures come as part of a
OL,11,Fpreviously announced "turnaround
OL,12,Foversight regime" floated by Ofwat for
OL,13,FThames last month.
OL,15,FThe regulator also opposed the
OL,16,Fcompany's planned 44% rise in consumer
OL,17,Fbills over the next five years,
OL,18,Ftelling Thames it should instead
OL,19,Fincrease average yearly bills by 23%
OL,20,Fto #535 over the period.
