OL,3,COfwat planning independent monitor for
OL,4,CThames Water after ratings downgrades
OL,6,FThames Water is in the grip of a
OL,7,Ffunding crisis and has more than #15
OL,8,Fbillion of debt. It said in July that
OL,9,Fit only has enough money to continue
OL,10,Ftrading until the end of May 2025.
OL,12,FBosses are scrambling to secure a
OL,13,Fmajor cash injection to keep it
OL,14,Fafloat, and have held talks with both
OL,15,Fexisting shareholders and outside
OL,16,Finvestors.
