OL,3,COfwat planning independent monitor for
OL,4,CThames Water after ratings downgrades
OL,6,FThe penalties relate to water firms'
OL,7,Fmanagement of their wastewater
OL,8,Ftreatment and sewer systems, which
OL,9,Fhave come under heavy criticism for
OL,10,Freleasing too much pollution into
OL,11,Frivers.
OL,13,FA spokesman for Thames Water said: "We
OL,14,Fnote that Ofwat is minded to accept
OL,15,Fthe undertakings we have proposed, but
OL,16,Funderstand the need for them to
OL,17,Fconsult before doing so.
